---
title: Pork Meatballs in Creamy Chive Sauce with chips and green beans
description: Oven-baked pork meatballs are cooked to juicy perfection then smothered in a creamy chive-infused sauce and served up alongside crisp green beans and hand-cut chips for a classic and comforting weeknight meal.
